**Stripe fees are lower when processing payments with Outseta**

Whether you’re using other membership software—or “just using Stripe”—you’ll pay additional under-the-hood fees for “Stripe Billing.” You won’t pay these fees with Outseta—saving you an additional .7% on every transaction.
